## Technical

### Blocks

- App (user interface)
- API (core logic)
- DB (data storage)

### Packages

- api (server)
- cor (core logic dependency to api)
- com (common dependencies to api and app)
- app (client)
- doc (project documentation)

### Technologies

- HTML / CSS  / JS
- Node
- Express
- React
- React Router
- Mongodb
- Mongoose
- Bcrypt
- TailwindCSS
- JWT

### Data Model

USER
- ID (auto)
- Name (string)
- Surname (string)
- Email (string)
- Username (string)
- Password (string)
- Avatar (string)
- Role (string, enum: project / investor)
- Title (string)
- PhoneNumber (string)
- Image (string)
- Description (string)
- Category (string)
- StartDate (date)
- EndDate (date)
- BudgetGoal (number)
- Match ([User.id])
- Likes ([User.id])

CHAT
- id (auto)
- Participants ([User.id])
- Messages ([Message.id])
- Date (date)

Message 

- id (auto)
- Author (User.id)
- Message (string)
- Date (date)
- Chat (Chat.id)


